tweet: #Disha got bail. Good for her. Good for democratic values. She is upper caste. #NodeepKaur did not get bail.  Bad for her, Bad for all women Bad for democratic values. She is a Dalit.  This dispensation of justice on basis of victims caste has to change . #ReleaseNodeepKaur
